OL,3,CPokemon card burglar appears in court
OL,5,FA Pokemon card thief has appeared in
OL,6,Fcourt following a string of shop
OL,7,Fthefts in Newark.
OL,9,FBenjamin Young, of Barrow Gate in
OL,10,FNewark, broke a window to get into a
OL,11,Frestaurant on Paxtons Court on 5 April.
OL,13,FHe then smashed a glass cabinet and
OL,14,Fhelped himself to stacks of Pokemon
OL,15,Fand Dragon ball cards as well as
OL,16,Felectrical products, food and drink.
OL,18,FThe damage he caused during the break-
OL,19,Fin left the owners more than #2000 out
OL,20,Fof pocket.
OL,26,@kD@DrrmD@FrrvD@`rr
