PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1778529954
OL,3,CPokemon card burglar appears in court
OL,5,FYoung, 47, later admitted to the
OL,6,Fburglary and ten shop thefts which
OL,7,Ftook place from March to May.
OL,9,FHe targeted seven shops in total
OL,10,Fstealing a mixture of alcohol, food,
OL,11,Fwashing up products and clothes.
OL,13,FYoung had already been charged and
OL,14,Fbailed for the first five thefts but
OL,15,Fchose not to attend court in April.
OL,17,FHaving known what he looked like,
OL,18,FNottinghamshire Police officers then
OL,19,Flinked Young to his further offences
OL,20,Fand arrested him again on 6 May. He
OL,21,Fpleaded guilty the following day.
OL,26,@kD@Drr
