PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1778529954
OL,3,CPokemon card burglar appears in court
OL,5,FHe remains in custody until he is due
OL,6,Fto be sentenced at Nottingham Crown
OL,7,FCourt on 28 May.
OL,9,FInspector Charlotte Ellam said: "This
OL,10,Fisn't the first time Benjamin Young
OL,11,Fhas found himself in trouble for
OL,12,Fstealing in our town.
OL,14,F"He's a prolific thief, responsible
OL,15,Ffor numerous shop thefts, who clearly
OL,16,Fthinks the laws don't apply to him.
OL,26,@kD@Drr
